sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as JavaFX UI
    participant VM as ViewModel
    participant AS as Application Services
    participant TE as Transaction Entry Module
    participant DAL as Data Access Layer
    participant DB as Local Database

    User->>UI: Enter transaction details
    User->>UI: Submit transaction
    UI->>VM: Pass entered data
    VM->>VM: Validate fields

    alt Validation fails
        VM-->>UI: Return validation errors
        UI-->>User: Display error messages
    else Validation succeeds
        VM->>AS: Request transaction save
        AS->>TE: Process transaction
        TE-->>AS: Validated transaction object
        AS->>DAL: Save transaction
        DAL->>DB: Insert record
        DB-->>DAL: Save confirmation
        DAL-->>AS: Persistence successful
        AS-->>VM: Return success/status
        VM-->>UI: Update UI state
        UI-->>User: Show confirmation and refresh summary
    end